{"tid":2029394,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【國安法】指美國面臨巨大政治壓力   BBC：或終止香港特殊待遇","createTime":"2020-05-22T08:12:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T09:10:28.000Z","uid":79563,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e5b717157e151f6352c2d6a8690f2c85409fcef0","tid":2029394,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:12:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xUI3A5YuShlD8v9bOuOUWw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200522a134203.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FxUI3A5YuShlD8v9bOuOUWw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20200522a134203.jpg&h=0ce22ce1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】全國人大計劃審議港區國安法，美國總統特朗普指，中國政府若在香港推行《國安法》，美國將作出強烈回應。BBC中文網引述分析人士稱，此舉可能導致美國終止對港特殊待遇。<br />\n<br />\n智庫戰略暨國際研究中心（CSIS）中國研究主任白明（Jude Blanchette）指，國安法可能導致美國終止香港的特殊待遇，將香港與中國同等對待。白明認為，華盛頓面臨巨大政治壓力，不太可能繼續認定香港仍享有足夠自治。但他指出，還需觀望《國安法》的具體措辭，來估量美方舉措。<br />\n<br />\n國安法將包括顛覆國家政權、分裂國家、恐怖活動、以及外部勢力干預，預計議案將在下周四表決，最快在今年8月在香港實施。"},{"pid":"9ec84e09262aa522a7cdf2f093aa022a4edf092d","tid":2029394,"uid":125502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q9CwkZO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ9CwkZO.jpg&h=c174bfaa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n還記得去年的盛夏？<br />\n差不多六月時分<br />\n今年的盛夏<br />\n差不多六月時分<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">繼續守護我城</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4d6d438d59dc445ff8cf46f2eae46f227570b930","tid":2029394,"uid":172349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:15:55.000Z","msg":"到時香港人自焚都無人會理"},{"pid":"9dfa3294c910f549e3ebb36f4ad279e4cfb1a436","tid":2029394,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-